The paper deals with the problem of reconstructing sparse signals from binary measurements, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SP), and mathematical modeling (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the application of the method to logistic regression, which falls under the category of statistical inference (cs.SI).
